{"tid":904651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 3 和記電訊成L日寄信黎我屋企恐嚇我屈我錢, 點算好啊><?","createTime":"2018-11-16T13:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T16:18:18.000Z","uid":189870,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8dfe24513fc473c171f21c71f78ef8b6ca6d98","tid":904651,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"小妹第一次上lihkg 開po, 如果講得19999請各位多多包涵<br />\n我系3 嘅舊客戶,上年4/5/6月時佢sales team不斷打電話唻騷擾我sell我續約, 但系因為佢加左我價所以我一直hold住冇應承, 期間我只系打過比佢地&quot;查詢&quot;條款,而並非承認簽約<br />\n咁我最後揀左中移動,一來佢customer service優質好多(唔會好似3咁成q日打去冇人聽),二來$平一大截<br />\n直到上個月, 3 嘅財政部send 信比我話我欠佢地$3903.14 (我明明每月準時交費ga wor), 我打左好耐終於打通(佢地客服成日打唔通), 原來係違約罰款, 話我同佢續約但搵第二間<br />\n<strong><strong><strong>乜我有同佢地有續過約咩?</strong></strong></strong><br />\n<strong><strong><strong>系冇arrrr!!!!!!</strong></strong></strong><br />\n之後銷售部staff 打唻扮死狗道歉話get 錯<br />\n以為件事會完<br />\n點知我啱啱收到信, 間野委托左商業顧問公司收我數, otw pass 去小額錢債法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我打極佢個hotline都打唔通,仲一味推來推去<br />\n我真系覺得好無助啊, 點算好吖? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想喊吖<br />\n各位師兄,點算好啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce6e81ed1fd5d2eb97b04768b133d987d5f8c38","tid":904651,"uid":84551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1867f09ac86e689a344fac1a97aefb5fa0668f91","tid":904651,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"講証據架嘛<br />\n<br />\n問佢拿返錄音囉<br />\n<br />\n無仲講乜姐"},{"pid":"ce474e09cc798c853a9ba2cd52ab57f38d74aaf6","tid":904651,"uid":189870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1867f09ac86e689a344fac1a97aefb5fa0668f91","tid":904651,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"講証據架嘛<br 